\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)^2 = \left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)\cdot\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right) = (a_0+a_1+\dots + a_n)\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)=\\=a_0\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)+a_1\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)+\dots+a_n\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right) =\\ =\left(\sum_{l=0}^na_l\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\right)\right) = \left(\sum_{l=0}^n\left(\sum_{k=0}^n a_ka_l\right)\right)
